                        "name": "Ravage",
                        "type": "offensive_action",
                        "text": "The intellect devourer makes two talon Strikes against a <a aonid=\"28\" game-obj=\"Conditions\">paralyzed</a>, <a aonid=\"33\" game-obj=\"Conditions\">restrained</a>, or <a aonid=\"38\" game-obj=\"Conditions\">unconscious</a> creature, using the same attack modifier as its highest attack modifier. These Strikes gain the <a aonid=\"40\" game-obj=\"Traits\">death</a> trait. If Ravage kills the target, the intellect devourer may use Body Thief against it as a free action.",
